enum aiDefaultLogStream

Enumerates predefined log streaming destinations. Logging to these streams can be enabled with a single call to LogStream::createDefaultStream.

Enumerator:
aiDefaultLogStream_FILE  Stream the log to a file
aiDefaultLogStream_STDOUT  Stream the log to std::cout
aiDefaultLogStream_STDERR  Stream the log to std::cerr
aiDefaultLogStream_DEBUGGER  MSVC only: Stream the log the the debugger (this relies on OutputDebugString from the Win32 SDK)

enum aiOrigin

Seek origins (for the virtual file system API). Much cooler than using SEEK_SET, SEEK_CUR or SEEK_END.

Enumerator:
aiOrigin_SET  Beginning of the file
aiOrigin_CUR  Current position of the file pointer
aiOrigin_END  End of the file, offsets must be negative
